snippet.title: Mufasa: The Lion King | Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
A lion who would change our lives forever. #Mufasa: The Lion King, in theaters December 20.

‚ÄúMufasa: The Lion King‚Äù enlists Rafiki to relay the legend of Mufasa to young lion cub Kiara, daughter of Simba and Nala, with Timon and Pumbaa lending their signature schtick. Told in flashbacks, the story introduces Mufasa as an orphaned cub, lost and alone until he meets a sympathetic lion named Taka‚Äîthe heir to a royal bloodline. The chance meeting sets in motion an expansive journey of an extraordinary group of misfits searching for their destiny‚Äîtheir bonds will be tested as they work together to evade a threatening and deadly foe.  
 
New and returning cast members were called on to lend their voices to the film:
- Aaron Pierre as Mufasa
- Kelvin Harrison Jr. as Taka, a lion prince with a bright future who accepts Mufasa into his family as a brother
- Tiffany Boone as Sarabi
- Kagiso Lediga as Young Rafiki
- Preston Nyman as Zazu
- Mads Mikkelsen as Kiros, a formidable lion with big plans for his pride 
- Thandiwe Newton as Taka‚Äôs mother, Eshe
- Lennie James as Taka‚Äôs father, Obasi 
- Anika Noni Rose as Mufasa‚Äôs mother, Afia
- Keith David as Mufasa‚Äôs father, Masego
- John Kani as Rafiki
- Seth Rogen as Pumbaa
- Billy Eichner as Timon
- Donald Glover as Simba
- Introducing Blue Ivy Carter as Kiara, daughter of King Simba and Queen Nala
- And Beyonc√© Knowles-Carter as Nala
 
Additional casting includes Braelyn Rankins, Theo Somolu, Folake Olowofoyeku, Joanna Jones, Thuso Mbedu, Sheila Atim, Abdul Salis and Dominique Jennings.

‚ÄúMufasa: The Lion King,‚Äù the new film coming to theaters Dec. 20 explores the unlikely rise of the beloved king of the Pride Lands. The film has an all-star roster of talent bringing new and fan-favorite characters to life‚Äîplus, celebrated award-winning songwriter Lin-Manuel Miranda is writing the film‚Äôs songs produced by Mark Mancina and Miranda, with additional music and performances by Lebo M. 
 
Said Miranda, ‚ÄúElton John. Tim Rice. Hans Zimmer. Lebo M. Mark Mancina. Beyonc√©, Labrinth, Ilya Salmanzadeh. Beau Black, Ford Riley, the incredible music team on ‚ÄòThe Lion Guard,‚Äô and so many musical contributors over the years. ‚ÄòThe Lion King‚Äô has an incredible musical legacy with music from some of the greatest songwriters around, and I'm humbled and proud to be a part of it. It's been a joy working alongside Barry Jenkins to bring Mufasa's story to life, and we can't wait for audiences to experience this film in theaters."
 
Blending live-action filmmaking techniques with photoreal computer-generated imagery, ‚ÄúMufasa: The Lion King‚Äù is directed by Barry Jenkins, produced by Adele Romanski & Mark Ceryak, and executive produced by Peter Tobyansen.

--------------------------------------------------------

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Shiddat Episode 27 Teaser - Har Pal Geo
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Shiddat Episode 27 Teaser - 30th April 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?

snippet.description:
In this video, look at the all-new #Mahindra #XUV3X0, testing its driving dynamics, handling, performance, and more. Our detailed drive review covers every aspect you need to know before considering this #CompactSUV.

Tech Specification:

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal‚Äôs Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in 'Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance, as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

snippet.title: Complete CLASS 11th PHYSICS in 1 Shot | Concepts + Most Important Questions | NEET 2024
snippet.description:
NEET ENDGAME 2024 - https://physicswallah.onelink.me/ZAZB/ewyd5b26
For more Updates, PDF Notes, Tests, and Quizzes: https://t.me/Physics_Wallah_Official_Channel

üì≤ PW App/Website: https://physicswallah.onelink.me/ZAZB/PWAppWEb
üìö PW Store: https://physicswallah.onelink.me/ZAZB/iw6qdu3t
-------------------------------------------------------
Complete Class 11th Physics in 1 Shot! Dive into essential concepts and the most important questions for NEET 2024 preparation. Elevate your understanding and excel in Physics with confidence! üåü
-------------------------------------------------------
Batch Description

01. We will cover Physics, Chemistry, Botany, and Zoology.
02. Classes will be conducted for 7 days.
03. One  Lecture per day according to the schedule.
04. We will cover crisp theory, and question discussion via NEET Reflection.
05. Classes will be LIVE on the Physics Wallah - Alakh Pandey Channel.
06. PDF Notes of each Class will be uploaded on the PW App under NEET End Game Batch 2024.
07. It will cover NEET PYQs 
08. Free 3 NEET Replica Full Syllabus Test Series with their LIVE paper Discussion on Competition Wallah YT Channel.
09. The complete course will be accessible to all the students until the NEET 2024 Exam.
10. Classes starting from 27th April 2024.
11. Syllabus will end by 3rd May 2024.
12. The Lecture Schedule will be provided in the community post of  Physics Wallah - Alakh Pandey/Competition Wallah YT Channel and Announcement section of the Batch 
-------------------------------------------------------
Timestamps-
00:00 - Introduction 
06:16 - Today's goal
09:25 - Basic Maths
1:52:16 - Vector
2:42:30 - Units and measurement 
4:33:38 - Motion in a straight line 
5:57:44 - Motion in a plane
7:34:20 - Newton's laws of motion 
9:13:10 - Work, power and energy 
10:29:50 - Centre of mass and collision 
11:36:30 - Moment of Inertia 
11:47:45 - Thank You Bachhon!
-------------------------------------------------------
üìå For any Queries or Complaints visit: https://bit.ly/PW_Queries OR give a Missed Call on 07019-243-492
-------------------------------------------------------
#Physics #NEET #PhysicsWallah #NEET2024 #OneShot #MostImportantQuestions #PYQs #Concepts #Class11

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 4073: Taarak Ki Sundar Kavita
--------------------------------------------------------
Dr. Hathi informs Dr. Chaddha that Taarak has a headache because he didn't follow the diet food plan given by Anjali. Taarak's boss shares that his wife appreciated a poem he wrote for her. Later, the Gokuldham men share amusing stories about their wives' shopping adventures.

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni

snippet.title: Voice Of Vote | Election Song 2024 | J.Nivas IAS | Kakinada District | Yasaswi Kondepudi
snippet.description:
#voiceofvote
CHUNAV KA PARV DESH KA GARV 
election 2024 voter awareness song

https://www.instagram.com/collectorkakinada?igsh=MTUxMGs2MDgyM3BpaQ==
https://www.instagram.com/yasaswikondepudi_official?igsh=Y2xxMTBwNGd3cDJo&utm_source=qr
https://www.instagram.com/deokkdge2024?igsh=dXVuOWRkZW4zd2xq&utm_source=qr

Step into the heart of democracy with our latest music video, "Voice Of Vote ," a stirring anthem dedicated to voter awareness by Dr. Yasaswi Kondepudi 
"Voice Of Vote ," a soul-stirring tribute to voter awareness initiatives inaugurated by Sri J.Nivas, IAS, Collector & District Election Officer, Kakinada District.
In a world where every vote counts, "Voice Of Vote " resonates as a powerful call to action, urging voters to exercise their fundamental right to vote. 
Through soul-stirring lyrics and captivating melodies, this song embodies the essence of democracy and the significance of active participation in the electoral process.
Join us on a journey of enlightenment as we shine a spotlight on the importance of voter awareness. From highlighting key issues to encouraging voter registration and turnout, "Voice Of Vote " serves as a rallying cry for civic engagement and empowerment.

music director & singer : Yasaswi Kondepudi
lyrics : alaraju {Hyderbad}
choreographer : Bhushan master {Banglore}
dop : Bhargav {Hyderbad} 
Editor : pavan Kopalli 
Rhythm programming : Sai ram pyla
Melody programming : yasaswi kondepudi
Mix and mastering : yasaswi kondepudi

snippet.title: Mahindra XUV 3XO - XUV300 Pro Max? | First Look
snippet.description: Here's all you need to know about the newly launched Mahindra XUV3X0 which is essentially a mid-life update of the XUV300. Though it still has the same platform and engine options, it now gets several new features including ADAS level 2, 360 degree camera, 6-airbags and ESC as standard, new 17-inch alloy wheels and a new 6-speed automatic gearbox. It also has received major changes on the inside, thanks to the new 10.3-inch touchscreen display with harmon kardon music system, electronic parking brake, 65Watt supported type C among others. All these features make it one of the most loaded cars in its segment. And the best part is its revised pricing, despite newer features it costs less than before as it starts at Rs 7.49 lacs and the top-end variant costs Rs 15.49 lacs (ex-showroom).

Shiddat Digitally Presented by Cerelac

Asra, a beautiful and cherished young woman, has led a life filled with love and care from her family. In contrast, Sultan, a determined and charismatic perfectionist, overcomes the challenges of his troubled childhood to consistently achieve his desires.

Despite their stark personality differences, Asra falls in love with Sultan. However, after they marry, Asra realizes that Sultan is not the ideal man she had envisioned. To please him, she sacrifices her desires and undergoes a significant transformation.

This revelation becomes the catalyst for an unending series of problems between them. The journey through marital life becomes a complex maze as Asra and Sultan attempt to navigate challenges, each trying to mold the other according to their own will and preference.

Will Asra and Sultan change for each other, or will the growing list of problems between them persist? When Asra discovers the reality about Sultan, how will she react? Is Sultan contemplating leaving Asra? Can love overcome all obstacles, or are some differences too profound to bridge?
